{"image_id": "PHM_2001_page_34", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "7 .  S T O C K  C O M P E N S AT I O N  P L A N S  A N D", "bbox": [112.5, 224.5, 505.7, 241.1]}, {"text": "M A N A G E M E N T  I N C E N T I V E  C O M P E N S AT I O N", "bbox": [112.5, 249.5, 541.8, 266.1]}, {"text": "The Company has fixed stock option plans for both employ-", "bbox": [112.5, 285.4, 612.5, 304.1]}, {"text": "ees (the “Employee Plans”) and for nonemployee directors", "bbox": [112.5, 310.4, 612.5, 329.1]}, {"text": "(the “Director Plans”); information related to the Plans is", "bbox": [112.5, 335.4, 618.1, 354.1]}, {"text": "as follows:", "bbox": [112.5, 360.3, 197.4, 379.1]}, {"text": "Shares", "bbox": [566.5, 382.8, 612.5, 399.5]}, {"text": "Plan Name", "bbox": [112.5, 403.6, 188.9, 420.3]}, {"text": "Authorized", "bbox": [533.8, 403.6, 612.5, 420.3]}, {"text": "Employee plans", "bbox": [112.5, 434.9, 236.1, 451.6]}, {"text": "Pulte Corporation 2000 Stock Incentive Plan", "bbox": [112.5, 457.8, 432.4, 474.5]}, {"text": "for Key Employees", "bbox": [131.0, 480.7, 262.5, 497.4]}, {"text": "2,500,000", "bbox": [538.4, 480.7, 612.5, 497.4]}, {"text": "Pulte Corporation 1995 Stock Incentive Plan", "bbox": [112.5, 503.6, 432.4, 520.3]}, {"text": "for Key Employees", "bbox": [131.0, 526.6, 262.5, 543.2]}, {"text": "4,000,000", "bbox": [538.4, 526.6, 612.5, 543.2]}, {"text": "Pulte Corporation 1994 Stock Incentive Plan", "bbox": [112.5, 549.5, 432.4, 566.1]}, {"text": "for Key Employees", "bbox": [131.0, 572.4, 262.5, 589.1]}, {"text": "2,000,000", "bbox": [538.4, 572.4, 612.5, 589.1]}, {"text": "Pulte Corporation 1990 Stock Incentive Plan", "bbox": [112.5, 595.3, 432.4, 612.0]}, {"text": "for Key Employees", "bbox": [131.0, 618.2, 262.5, 634.9]}, {"text": "1,600,000", "bbox": [538.4, 618.2, 612.5, 634.9]}, {"text": "Nonemployee director plans", "bbox": [112.5, 641.1, 334.4, 657.8]}, {"text": "2000 Stock Plan for Nonemployee Directors", "bbox": [112.5, 664.1, 424.7, 680.7]}, {"text": "250,000", "bbox": [552.3, 664.1, 612.5, 680.7]}, {"text": "1997 Stock Plan for Nonemployee Directors", "bbox": [112.5, 687.0, 424.7, 703.6]}, {"text": "133,400", "bbox": [552.3, 687.0, 612.5, 703.6]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2001, 801,000 stock options remain avail-", "bbox": [112.5, 722.9, 612.4, 741.6]}, {"text": "able for grant under the Employee Plans and 201,000 stock", "bbox": [112.5, 747.9, 612.5, 766.6]}, {"text": "options remain available for grant under the Director Plans.", "bbox": [112.5, 772.9, 588.9, 791.6]}, {"text": "The Employee Plans provide for the grant of options (both", "bbox": [662.5, 224.4, 1162.5, 243.2]}, {"text": "non-qualified options and incentive stock options as defined in", "bbox": [662.5, 249.4, 1162.5, 268.2]}, {"text": "each respective plan), stock appreciation rights and restricted", "bbox": [662.5, 274.4, 1162.5, 293.2]}, {"text": "stock to key employees of the Company or its subsidiaries (as", "bbox": [662.5, 299.4, 1162.5, 318.2]}, {"text": "determined by the Compensation Committee of the Board of", "bbox": [662.5, 324.4, 1162.5, 343.2]}, {"text": "Directors) for periods not exceeding 10 years. Options granted", "bbox": [662.5, 349.4, 1162.5, 368.2]}, {"text": "under the Employee Plans vest incrementally in periods rang-", "bbox": [662.5, 374.4, 1162.5, 393.2]}, {"text": "ing from six months to five years. Under the Director Plans,", "bbox": [662.5, 399.4, 1162.5, 418.2]}, {"text": "each new nonemployee director will receive 900 shares of", "bbox": [662.5, 424.4, 1162.5, 443.2]}, {"text": "common stock and options to purchase an additional 4,000", "bbox": [662.5, 449.4, 1162.5, 468.2]}, {"text": "shares. Nonemployee directors are also entitled to an annual", "bbox": [662.5, 474.4, 1162.5, 493.2]}, {"text": "distribution of 900 shares of common stock and options to", "bbox": [662.5, 499.4, 1162.5, 518.2]}, {"text": "purchase an additional 4,000 shares. All options granted are", "bbox": [662.5, 524.4, 1162.5, 543.2]}, {"text": "non-qualified, vest immediately and are exercisable on the", "bbox": [662.5, 549.4, 1162.5, 568.2]}, {"text": "date of grant. Options granted under the Director Plans are", "bbox": [662.5, 574.4, 1162.5, 593.2]}, {"text": "exercisable for 10 years from the grant date.", "bbox": [662.5, 599.4, 1020.7, 618.2]}, {"text": "As a result of the Del Webb merger, the Company assumed", "bbox": [662.5, 636.9, 1162.5, 655.7]}, {"text": "Del Webb’s employee stock plans and their director stock", "bbox": [662.5, 661.9, 1162.5, 680.7]}, {"text": "plans. No stock options remain available for grant under the", "bbox": [662.5, 686.9, 1162.5, 705.7]}, {"text": "Del Webb plans.", "bbox": [662.5, 711.9, 794.5, 730.7]}, {"text": "Pulte Homes 2001 Annual Report", "bbox": [900.0, 1574.5, 1133.4, 1589.1]}, {"text": "37", "bbox": [1169.0, 1574.5, 1186.0, 1589.1]}, {"text": "A summary of the status of the Company’s stock option plans as of December 31, 2001, 2000 and 1999 and changes during the", "bbox": [112.5, 832.7, 1162.5, 851.5]}, {"text": "years ending on those dates is presented below (000’s omitted):", "bbox": [112.5, 857.7, 626.3, 876.5]}, {"text": "2001", "bbox": [576.3, 894.8, 613.3, 911.5]}, {"text": "2000", "bbox": [817.9, 894.8, 855.0, 911.5]}, {"text": "1999", "bbox": [1053.9, 894.8, 1090.9, 911.5]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [603.3, 926.0, 685.4, 942.7]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [846.1, 926.0, 920.8, 942.7]}, {"text": "Weighted-", "bbox": [1083.6, 926.0, 1158.3, 942.7]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [620.2, 946.9, 685.4, 963.5]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [862.8, 946.9, 920.8, 963.5]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [1100.3, 946.9, 1158.3, 963.5]}, {"text": "Per Share", "bbox": [611.1, 967.7, 685.4, 984.4]}, {"text": "Per Share", "bbox": [854.0, 967.7, 920.8, 984.4]}, {"text": "Per Share", "bbox": [1091.5, 967.7, 1158.3, 984.4]}, {"text": "Shares", "bbox": [502.6, 988.5, 554.2, 1005.2]}, {"text": "Exercise Price", "bbox": [580.6, 988.5, 685.4, 1005.2]}, {